    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a very powerful way to frame it. My students can definitely use that wording. \n\nTo make sure they are fully prepared, they also need to anticipate the most difficult counter-arguments. Often, the opposition will try to frame these security measures as being fundamentally inhumane or driven by xenophobia. How should my students respond to the claim that strict enforcement is actually a violation of basic human rights and international humanitarian principles?",
